		{ ref: `Psalm 46:5`, slug: `psalms`, ch: 46, text: `Your Father is in the midst of her; she shall not be moved; God will help her when morning dawns.`, note: `You are not holding this family together alone. He is in the middle of your home, and help comes with the dawn.` },
	]}
	offersHeading={`What "our Father" offers you`}
	offersIntroHtml={`New parenthood asks you to give and give until there's nothing left. Here's what your Father gives you instead — for free, because you're already His.`}
	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `Strength when you're running on empty`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to summon it from somewhere inside: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/40" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father gives strength to the weary</a> and power to those who feel like they have none left to give.` },
		{ heading: `Somewhere to put the worry`, bodyHtml: `Every fear about the baby, the future, whether you're doing it right — <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/1-peter/5" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">cast all your anxiety on Him</a>, because He genuinely cares for you and for them.` },
		{ heading: `Mercy that resets every morning`, bodyHtml: `However the last 24 hours went, you wake up to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/lamentations/3" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">mercies that are new every morning</a> — no guilt carried over, no scoreboard from yesterday.` },
		{ heading: `The truth that your child is a gift`, bodyHtml: `On the hardest days, remember: this little life is <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/127" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">a heritage and reward from your Father</a>, placed into your arms on purpose, by a God who knit them together.` },
	]}
	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for new parents`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father — so you can parent from being parented`, bodyHtml: `Most Bibles can read like a rulebook of expectations — the last thing an exhausted new parent needs. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does, from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. You're not handed one more standard to meet; you're met by the Father whose love you can pour out onto your child.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio for the 3am feedings`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen one-handed while you feed the baby, rock them back to sleep, or sit in the dark wondering if you're doing okay. The Father's voice fits into your real day and night.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to the exhaustion and the anxiety`, bodyHtml: `Worn out? Worried? Wondering if you're enough? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to talk to Him in the in-between moments with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where you are, even on no sleep.` },
